From: Theophilus Afum <tafum@noguchi.ug.edu.gh>
Date: Sat, 20 Jun 2026 14:20:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Remove hardcoded paths; make scripts portable for reuse

- Replace machine-specific absolute paths (/home/tafum, /mnt/c/Users/theop)
  with relative defaults overridable via environment variables
- R scripts: Sys.getenv(VAR, relative_default); shell: ${VAR:-relative_default}
- 04_magma_analysis.sh: resolve input/output paths to absolute before cd
- Make nested output dirs created with recursive=TRUE
- 01_qc_pipeline.qmd: genericize example paths to $HOME / relative
- README: fix contact email typo, fix clone URL, update script list to match
  actual files, add Configuration/paths section
- Fill in author placeholder in 03_case_case_gwas.sh
